"title": "5731: parents",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5731",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture stipulates that children should show respect and concern for their parents.</p>\n<h2>Honouring parents</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:12\">EXO 20:12</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:16\">DEU 5:16</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:3\">LEV 19:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:22\">PRO 23:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:16-Matt19:19\">MAT 19:16–19:19</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:17-Mark10:19\">MRK 10:17–10:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:18-Luke18:20\">LUK 18:18–18:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:1-Eph6:3\">EPH 6:1–6:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:20\">COL 3:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:4\">1TI 5:4</a></p>\n<h2>Dishonouring parents</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:1-2Tim3:2\">2TI 3:1–3:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:15-Exod21:17\">EXO 21:15–21:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:18-Deut21:21\">DEU 21:18–21:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:7\">EZK 22:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:1-Matt15:9\">MAT 15:1–15:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:1-Mark7:13\">MRK 7:1–7:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:28-Rom1:32\">ROM 1:28–1:32</a></p>\n<h2>Love between parents and children can be suppressed</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:16-Luke21:17\">LUK 21:16–21:17</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:21\">MAT 10:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:12\">MRK 13:12</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech13:2-Zech13:3\">ZEC 13:2–13:3</a></p>\n<h2>Love for God must surpass love for parents</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:26\">LUK 14:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:8-Deut33:11\">DEU 33:8–33:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:28-Luke18:30\">LUK 18:28–18:30</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:27-Matt19:29\">MAT 19:27–19:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:28-Mark10:30\">MRK 10:28–10:30</a></p>\n<h2>Divine love surpasses parental love</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:10\">PSA 27:10</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The belief that children were punished for their parents' sins</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:1-John9:3\">JHN 9:1–9:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:5-Exod20:6\">EXO 20:5–20:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:9-Deut5:10\">DEU 5:9–5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:19-Job21:21\">JOB 21:19–21:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:1-Ezek18:4\">EZK 18:1–18:4</a></p>\n<h2>Parents caring for their children</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:14\">2CO 12:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:14\">PRO 19:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:24-Prov23:25\">PRO 23:24–23:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:23\">HEB 11:23</a></p>\n<h2>Children caring for their parents</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam22:3-1Sam22:4\">1SA 22:3–22:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:8-Josh2:20\">JOS 2:8–2:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:22-Josh6:23\">JOS 6:22–6:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:6\">PRO 17:6</a></p>\n<h2>Mourning for parents</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:1-Lev21:2\">LEV 21:1–21:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:10-Lev21:11\">LEV 21:10–21:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:2-Num6:7\">NUM 6:2–6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:10-Deut21:13\">DEU 21:10–21:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:25\">EZK 44:25</a></p>\n<h2>Parents and the marriage of their children</h2>\n<h3>A man leaves his parents to marry his wife</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:21-Gen2:24\">GEN 2:21–2:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:3-Matt19:6\">MAT 19:3–19:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:2-Mark10:9\">MRK 10:2–10:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25-Eph5:33\">EPH 5:25–5:33</a></p>\n<h3>Parents were responsible for vindicating their daughter's reputation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:13-Deut22:19\">DEU 22:13–22:19</a></p>\n<h3>Sometimes parents jointly arranged their children's marriages</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:1-Judg14:3\">JDG 14:1–14:3</a></strong></p>",
